{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1681-02_106","head":{"value":"[Metamorphose d’Alectrion en Coq]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", février 1681 [tome 2], p. 106-111.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Je passe à d’autres amours dont le recit vous plaira, quoy que l’Avanture n’ait rien de nouveau pour vous. Il est naturel, &amp; d’une Muse qui a des expressions aisées. Peut-estre avez-vous quelques Amies dans vostre Province, qui s’éveillant quelquefois au chant du Coq, ne sçavent pas que la necessité de se faire entendre quand le jour approche, est un châtiment qu’il s’est attiré. Ce petit Ouvrage est d’une Personne de qualité, dont le mérite répond à l’esprit.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"label":{"value":"METAMORPHOSE D’ALECTRION EN COQ.","id":"/div/quote/label"},"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Conte dit que le Dieu Mars,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rebuté comme un vieux Gendarme","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De la fatigue &amp; des hazards","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que la Guerre de toutes parts","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Traîne avec de si grands vacarmes,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Résolut de se reposer,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et pour se divertir, voulut galantiser.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Suivant ce beau dessein, dans l’Isle de Cythere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il choisit un Quartier de rafraîchissement.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Dame du Païs le reçeut galamment,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et luy fit, dit-on, chere entiere.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un soir qu’il avoit rendez-vous","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avecque son Hostesse aussi tendre que belle,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":"  ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De crainte des Filoux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":"  ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou du Mary jaloux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il se fit escorter par un Valet fidelle","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’on appelloit Alectrion,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’autant qu’en pareille affaire","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":"  ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un peu de précaution","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est toûjours fort necessaire :","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais comme le Dieu des Combats","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans-doute ne s’ennuyoit pas","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pres de la belle Cytherée,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il s’oublia dans les plaisirs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et la nuit toute entiere, au gré de ses desirs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Parut de fort courte durée.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cependant le Prince du Jour","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui soûpiroit pour la Déesse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans pouvoir gagner sa tendresse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plein d’inquiétude &amp; d’amour,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Remonta sur nostre Hémisphere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un peu plus-tost qu’à l’ordinaire.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ses rayons curieux, fort indiscretement","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Entrerent trop matin dans un Apartement,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où le Galant &amp; la Belle","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Parloient de leur passion,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car le pauvre Alectrion","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’endormit en sentinelle.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il en fut aussi battu","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une terrible maniere ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son Maître estoit si bourru,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il eut cent coups d’étriviere.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin dans le couroux dont Mars fut embrazé","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[42]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par cette funeste avanture,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le pauvre Alectrion fut métamorphosé.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On luy donna d’un Coq la forme &amp; la figure ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[45]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[46]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais en changeant de nature,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[46]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[47]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il se fit plus avisé,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[47]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[48]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car sa disgrace passée","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[48]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[49]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans cesse occupant sa pensée,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[49]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[50]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On voit toûjours dés le minuit","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[50]/hi/#"}}},{"#1":{"value":"(","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[51]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Bien que dans l’Univers tout repose sans bruit","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[51]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":")","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[51]/#2"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que quand l’Astre du Jour veut quiter l’autre monde","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[52]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour rendre à celuy-cy sa lumiere féconde,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[53]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[54]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dés qu’il approche l’Horizon,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[54]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Coq se souvenant du sort d’Alectrion,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[55]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[56]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aussitost se met à l’erte,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[56]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[57]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et chantant à gorge ouverte,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[57]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[58]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’un empressement nompareil,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[58]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il annonce aux Mortels le retour du Soleil.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[59]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je ne vous diray point si c’est Histoire ou Fable,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[60]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je le tiens cependant d’un Autheur approuvé ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[61]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[62]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si le cas n’est pas véritable,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[62]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[63]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il paroist assez bien trouvé.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[63]/hi/#"}}}]}}}}